text: Adriana Biagiotti (born 19 July 1947) is a retired Italian gymnast. She competed at the 1968 Olympics in all artistic gymnastics events with the best result of 39th place on the vault. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Gymnasts at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Italian female artistic gymnasts
